man command     - view help for a command

man -k keyword  - keyword search on installed manual pages (apropos)

coomand --help  -  get quick help on a command

whatis          - a quick method for searching the specified command or file in the man database for a short description

info command    - allow users to read command documentation

/usr/share/doc  - stores documentation for all installed packages under sub-directories that match package names followed by their
-<version>

